        <abstract> 
<p>Sends <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> to FJP. "I rest my conviction solely on the fact, as it seems to me, that the theory explains large classes of facts otherwise inexplicable." Has made important converts: Lyell, Hooker, Huxley, and W. B. Carpenter.</p> 
